snippet.title: The Nameless: Slay Dragon Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2410170/_/

The turn-based RPG "The Nameless One: Dragon Slayer" in late development.

Plot rich, no bright and dark thunder, not water length, multiple endings.

Five years a sword, add to wishlist if you are interested!
